{"tid":925730,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"日本長年赤字動物園堅持營運　","createTime":"2018-12-03T03:02:30.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-04T06:34:02.000Z","uid":184679,"like":56,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"c9504cf72efa07f59a82ee647a74d3a72cc9f082","tid":925730,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T03:02:30.000Z","msg":"位於日本三重縣的大內山動物園為少數的私人動物園，園長表示動物園財政一直都處於赤字狀態，只靠自己個人儲蓄支撐，到底是甚麼原因驅使他繼續營運呢？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2150516/org/0ec152bcacb0502a907cbe4bcec6bcd9.jpg/u4ZrrbDwYKxgo5WX-pgcutPHMk227lpB1VVXLtVVVy4?v=w1600\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2150516%2Forg%2F0ec152bcacb0502a907cbe4bcec6bcd9.jpg%2Fu4ZrrbDwYKxgo5WX-pgcutPHMk227lpB1VVXLtVVVy4%3Fv%3Dw1600&h=40af5fe0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n位置頗為偏僻<br />\n<br />\n日本節目《超可愛影像的連發》到訪大內山動物園，發現位置頗為偏僻，從最近的大內山JR站下車後，需要步行30分鐘才到... 不過園內動物種類不少，有114種動物，共724隻。還有突變種動物，十分可愛！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2150543/org/21f5c573206fc6767930b43a92e3478c.jpg/D-u36EWWEpMsc8-haoRu2_C6gCWAV9wuCwwRigsMEYo?v=w800\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2150543%2Forg%2F21f5c573206fc6767930b43a92e3478c.jpg%2FD-u36EWWEpMsc8-haoRu2_C6gCWAV9wuCwwRigsMEYo%3Fv%3Dw800&h=51251dd6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2150544/org/679d1bbd84ab545abd1035371faf4f62.jpg/1r-1pcrc9q3M-SjvaNvCpCymDG9xoiJCRkljxEZJY8Q?v=w800\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2150544%2Forg%2F679d1bbd84ab545abd1035371faf4f62.jpg%2F1r-1pcrc9q3M-SjvaNvCpCymDG9xoiJCRkljxEZJY8Q%3Fv%3Dw800&h=d67b7c1b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2150542/org/21c4fb79ecf3e074cd70666ab2ab5ecf.jpg/zuFXrbv-ytuEYIQ7RfOT3GVBe2nzy80JiR8Zo4kfGaM?v=w800\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2150542%2Forg%2F21c4fb79ecf3e074cd70666ab2ab5ecf.jpg%2FzuFXrbv-ytuEYIQ7RfOT3GVBe2nzy80JiR8Zo4kfGaM%3Fv%3Dw800&h=06b012fc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2150546/org/67c3f454b851d6c420a10263f9a2ed67.jpg/j1Xir1oUvOfTQ5_NtlrpVfQX_y_8tNv8uKlNF7ipTRc?v=w800\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2150546%2Forg%2F67c3f454b851d6c420a10263f9a2ed67.jpg%2Fj1Xir1oUvOfTQ5_NtlrpVfQX_y_8tNv8uKlNF7ipTRc%3Fv%3Dw800&h=515d854e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n動物園長年赤字，從沒賺過錢<br />\n<br />\n68歲的山本清號先生是大內山動物園園長，他於節目中表示這間動物園是日本少有的私人動物園，而且一直處於赤字狀態，靠著以往任職建築公司社長時儲下的積蓄才能繼續營運，68歲的他仍每天樂此不疲地親身照顧動物們。<br />\n<br />\n為保護動物而堅持<br />\n<br />\n每天辛勞地照顧動物，還要自己貼錢填補赤字，為何山本先生仍不選擇閉園呢？山本先生表示全因想給動物們一個「家」...<br />\n<br />\n點擊影片了解山本先生堅持原因 <a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E5%AF%B5%E7%89%A9/264954/%E6%97%A5%E6%9C%AC%E9%95%B7%E5%B9%B4%E8%B5%A4%E5%AD%97%E5%8B%95%E7%89%A9%E5%9C%92%E5%A0%85%E6%8C%81%E7%87%9F%E9%81%8B-%E7%9A%86%E5%9B%A0%E6%83%B3%E7%B5%A6%E8%A2%AB%E9%81%BA%E6%A3%84%E5%8B%95%E7%89%A9%E4%B8%80%E5%80%8B%E5%AE%B6\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E5%25AF%25B5%25E7%2589%25A9%2F264954%2F%25E6%2597%25A5%25E6%259C%25AC%25E9%2595%25B7%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E8%25B5%25A4%25E5%25AD%2597%25E5%258B%2595%25E7%2589%25A9%25E5%259C%2592%25E5%25A0%2585%25E6%258C%2581%25E7%2587%259F%25E9%2581%258B-%25E7%259A%2586%25E5%259B%25A0%25E6%2583%25B3%25E7%25B5%25A6%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E9%2581%25BA%25E6%25A3%2584%25E5%258B%2595%25E7%2589%25A9%25E4%25B8%2580%25E5%2580%258B%25E5%25AE%25B6&d=T4XM9PkblQOSe8zhi732TdU7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=ba328c8d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E5%AF%B5%E7%89%A9/264954/%E6%97%A5%E6%9C%AC%E9%95%B7%E5%B9%B4%E8%B5%A4%E5%AD%97%E5%8B%95%E7%89%A9%E5%9C%92%E5%A0%85%E6%8C%81%E7%87%9F%E9%81%8B-%E7%9A%86%E5%9B%A0%E6%83%B3%E7%B5%A6%E8%A2%AB%E9%81%BA%E6%A3%84%E5%8B%95%E7%89%A9%E4%B8%80%E5%80%8B%E5%AE%B6</a><br />\n<br />\n山本先生無私地接納失去依靠的動物們，拯救了數百條小生命，為牠們付出所有時間及金錢，真的十分偉大啊！希望動物園能夠盡快轉虧為盈吧！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2150548/org/1aa52e75754228ee2bd4b625f601bfd3.jpg/4fIHScXs2_59K-ZbzkitxYMYQvZ640YcsjCIz7IwiM8\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2150548%2Forg%2F1aa52e75754228ee2bd4b625f601bfd3.jpg%2F4fIHScXs2_59K-ZbzkitxYMYQvZ640YcsjCIz7IwiM8&h=c42bd890&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.oouchiyama-zoo.com/common/img/header/logo.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.oouchiyama-zoo.com%2Fcommon%2Fimg%2Fheader%2Flogo.png&h=78b554be&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n大内山動物園<br />\n<br />\n〒519-3111 三重県度会郡大紀町大内山530-4アクセス<br />\n【営業時間】9：00～16：00<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.oouchiyama-zoo.com/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.oouchiyama-zoo.com%2F&d=T4XM9PkblQOSe8zhi732TdU7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=6ef574db\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.oouchiyama-zoo.com/</a>"},{"pid":"dfe5be1dc4597762a877b5edf1bc5c3340e91a52","tid":925730,"uid":191815,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T03:03:29.000Z","msg":"三重本身都唔係觀光大県"},{"pid":"1b6b3a72875967e8de326ebaebe977cf05d049d3","tid":925730,"uid":184679,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"dfe5be1dc4597762a877b5edf1bc5c3340e91a52","tid":925730,"uid":191815,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T03:03:29.000Z","msg":"三重本身都唔係觀光大県"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T03:47:15.000Z","msg":"著名有伊勢神宮, 伊賀忍者, 海女<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26575f23d787492d1a90f21b8af7329d15ff2e20","tid":925730,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T05:10:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43d2e1e12692a48c5c012eaf72289582305f2462","tid":925730,"uid":91771,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"df